  "design_notes": "The chart leverages a solid syncopated rhythm throughout, matching the quick 184 BPM tempo of the track. To stay within the medium difficulty limits (especially the max sustained 5.0 NPS), the density transitions from simple 4th-note-centric movements in the intro and builds into syncopated 8th-note triplets and short streams in the main drop. Jumps are reserved strictly for key musical accents, and holds are woven into the synth-heavy phrases to create a satisfying physical flow that matches the energy curve.",
